            <li><span>Identification of the material on our servers that is claimed to be infringing and that is to be
            removed, including the URL or other information to enable us to locate the material.</span></li>
            <li><span>A statement that you have a good faith belief that use of the material in the manner
            complained of is not authorized by you as copyright owner, or by your agent, or by law.</span></li>
            <li><span>A statement that the information in your notice is accurate, and under penalty of perjury, that
            you are the owner (or authorized to act on behalf of the owner) of the exclusive copyright
